tract><style face="normal" font="default" size="100%">&lt;p&gt;This paper describes the participation of CERTH in the â€śSocialEvent Detection Task @ MediaEval 2011â€ť, which aimsat discovering social events in a large photo collection. Thetask comprises two challenges: (i) identification of soccerevents in the cities of Barcelona and Rome, and (ii) identificationof events taking place in two specific venues. Weadopt an approach that combines spatial and temporal filterswith tag-based location classification models and an ef-ficient photo clustering method. In our best runs, we achieveF-measure and NMI scores of 77.4% and 0.63 respectivelyfor Challenge 1, and 64% and 0.38 for Challenge 2.&lt;/p&gt;
